    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the iconic S54 3.2L straight-six engine. This unit features individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response and has undergone a comprehensive VANOS system refresh to ensure variable valve timing precision. The chassis is sorted with essential rear subframe reinforcement and a Bilstein B16 coilover suite, enhancing roll stiffness and damping control. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. While the exterior displays minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains tight with consistent compression across all cylinders. This is a driver-focused example optimized for longitudinal dynamics and apex hunting.",
      "price": 34500.0,
