    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkably well-maintained example that strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and pride of ownership. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though a close eye will find minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the passenger door\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All electronic features, from the responsive infotainment screen to the heated seats and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound and reflects a history of proactive care. It starts effortlessly, idles smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp. We have recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the brakes and tires have plenty of life remaining. This is an honest, dependable car that drives as beautifully as it looks.",
